info.name: Fatal Frame - Roblox
info.description: An interesting horror game by the looks of it, though admittedly a bit poor in graphics. This is a follow-up to a request, I fulfil most, so go ahead and describe the pic you want in the comments or send an imgur link to it. If you find a better-quality image put an imgur link to it in the comments. Low Quality Warning: The game is from 2001, that's pretty old so if you find a better image, do as I have said above and I'll try bumping it up. Credits to Fatal Frame, a horror game for not the lighthearted it seems, so I just put in the wikipedia link instead of the usual steam link. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
info.additionalInfo: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Won't work for tablets/iPads or phones. The style not appearing or downloading bug is an issue with the extension, not the style. Press 'Read more' for further help. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. Turkish Translated Help Section - Yardım bölümü Türkçe'ye çevrildi. French Translated Help Section - Section d'aide traduite en français - cliquez ici. Russian/Cyrillic Translated Help Section - Русский/кириллица переведенный раздел помощи - кликните сюда. Spanish Translated Help Section - Sección de ayuda traducida al español - haga clic aquí. A disclaimer: all the translations I make are just Google translated, I ain't no multilingual savant, so if there are any readers who are proficient in the languages above, please do tell me where I've messed up. 22 June 2023 - Released.
